understandable to everybody.

00:27:57.000 --> 00:27:59.440
So for that idiomatic phrase,
maybe not everyone knows it.

00:27:59.440 --> 00:28:02.600
But other things,
like May 35th, which

00:28:02.600 --> 00:28:06.070
